(9, 'A Q&amp;A with Sport: 80&#039;s Jonny Turner', 0, '', '', 'ed57413867ed9f2843cdd9e360b91a8b.png', '&lt;h2 glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;In this Q&amp;A we hear from Jonny Turner, Head of Operations at one of Yorkshire&#039;s most exciting start-ups and Northern Stars 2017 winners - Sport:80!&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.sport80.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Sport:80&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is an award-winning sports technology company based in Sheffield that combines extensive sports industry expertise and a highly talented in-house development team. Founded in 2012, Sport:80 has quickly established a reputation as one of the most exciting technology companies in its field and now works with sports organisations across the UK and United States.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;The company&rsquo;s flagship product, the Sport:80 Platform, is a proprietary sports CRM that enables sports organisations to work in more efficient, engaging and profitable ways. Uniquely the CRM enables sports organisations to manage numerous business operations from a single system whilst providing online services to athletes, coaches, officials and clubs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;What initially sparked the idea to start-up Sport:80?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;We first had the idea for Sport:80 in 2011 when myself and Gary, our CEO, worked together on a number of sporting events in the run up to the Olympic and Paralympic Games in London. During this time we realised how far behind the sport sector was in terms of the use of technology. Many event organisers and governing bodies were reliant on aging or disparate IT systems, and in some cases were still working from complex spreadsheets or paper-based systems. One of the major contributing factors to this problem was that there was a complete lack of technology that specifically catered for the operational or business management side of sport. So we incorporated Sport:80 and started work on our platform.&nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Who is Sport:80 aimed at? Who uses it?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;The Sport:80 Platform has been built for organisations that govern or manage sport. It&rsquo;s typically adopted by an International Federation, National Governing Body or Sports Club who use it to manage key areas of their organisations. Uniquely, the Platform can also be made available to participants &ndash; athletes, coaches, officials etc. &ndash; who can manage their personal involvement in the sport, such as purchasing their membership, entering competitions and managing their qualifications for example. We built the technology with this specific aim in mind; it was important that it could be used at every level to provide the governing body with an entire overview of their sport.&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Being a growing start-up, what challenges have you encountered so far and how have you overcome them?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;I think our biggest challenge has been around behavioural change. The reality is that people fear change and because our technology has an impact on so many areas of a sports organisation, these feelings are often amplified when we get in to the detail of a project. Quite early on in our journey we had to come up with a way to quell our client&rsquo;s fears and give them confidence in our technology and our people. This has actually resulted in what is arguably the most valuable element of our business model; our partnership approach. We invest a lot of time in establishing strong working relationships with all of our clients and we take the time to carefully guide them through every stage of a project. Once the Platform is live and in operation, we provide on-going support and a personal level of service that most organisations are not used to receiving when it comes to their technology.&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;You were winners at the&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://technorthhq.com/programmes/northern-stars/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Northern Stars&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;grand final! How did you find the Northern Stars process and how has it helped the growth of Sport:80?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;It&rsquo;s been fantastic to be a part of&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sport80.com/news/2017/sport80-a-northern-star&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Northern Stars&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and since the final it&rsquo;s been a bit of whirlwind. We were able to exhibit at the&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sport80.com/news/2017/hallo-from-berlin&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tech Crunch Disrupt&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;event in Berlin and have been involved in round-table events at the Department for Media, Culture and Sport. Part of our philosophy has always been that we are doing this because of our love of sport, and we have a passion to give back to it&nbsp; &ndash; being able to help influence thinking at government level is definitely something we have been really pleased to have been able to do. Hopefully we will continue to be included in conversations that can help to aid progress in both the sport and tech sectors!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;These kind of opportunities simply wouldn&rsquo;t have been available without the support from&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://technorthhq.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tech North&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and we are very grateful for the recognition and exposure.&nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;What would your advice be to other start-ups looking to get their business off the ground?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Have a big vision, a clear goal and don&rsquo;t be afraid to dream big! Being truly passionate about what you are doing will help you through when times get hard but will also shine through when you are promoting your company and product/service.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nWe set out on our journey with a passion to change the way our industry works, in order to help it progress and create opportunity for future generations. There&rsquo;s no way we would have received the level of support that we did from the outset if we didn&rsquo;t have this clear vision and obvious passion for what we were doing. Some of our earliest supporters made it clear that this solidified their belief in us and our ability to achieve what we promised. This passion combined with the successful implementation and continual improvement of our product is ensuring that we continue to grow year on year.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nSaying all of this, once you are up and running: be focussed and do everything you can to stay on a clear and defined path towards your goal. It is easy to get distracted by opportunity that sits outside of your natural product suite or development plan. Assess opportunity carefully and be brave enough to turn away offers that may hamper your ability to be the best at what you do.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Sport:80 is based in Sheffield. What do you like about the digital scene in Sheffield?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;It feels like Sheffield has been playing catch up to the likes of Leeds and Manchester for a long time, but it&rsquo;s really coming in to its own now. The city&rsquo;s digital scene is growing at a crazy rate but it hasn&rsquo;t lost that community-feel which is great. Take&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.simt.co.uk/kelham-island-museum&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Kelham Island&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;where we are based for example; just a short walk from our office you will find award-winning design agencies, app and game developers, and digital marketing specialists, all of which have set up home in old steel works and factories. Having so many innovative businesses on our doorstep is great as it creates so much potential for collaboration.&nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;What&rsquo;s next for Sport:80 in 2018?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;I think 2018 is going to be a huge year for us. Soon we will be announcing a significant partnership with one of the sport industry&rsquo;s biggest influencers, as well as a number of other partnerships and projects that we are very proud of. There will also be more to come from our work in the United States where we have established some great foundations. Our hope is that all of this will result in growing our team in Sheffield and attracting more tech talent to the city.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 1, '', '', '', 'a-q-a-with-sport-80-s-jonny-turner', 'yes', 'no', 1514592000);
INSERT INTO `blog` (`id`, `title`, `consultant_id`, `subtitle`, `subtitle2`, `image`, `content`, `content_before`, `sector`, `meta_title`, `meta_keywords`, `meta_desc`, `slug`, `posted`, `deleted`, `time`) VALUES
(10, 'A Q&amp;A with Web Development Consultant, Harry Roberts', 0, '', '', '0b514dc3675beebe4cf165676403e108.png', '&lt;h2 glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;In this Q&amp;A we hear from Leeds based Web Development Consultant, Harry Roberts. Here he tells us more about his career journey, being a Google Developer Expert and provides some insightful advice to young developers. Read more below...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hey, I&rsquo;m Harry. I&rsquo;m a&lt;a href=&quot;https://csswizardry.com/about/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Consultant Front-end Architect and Performance Engineer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;from Leeds. It&rsquo;s a bit of an obscure job title, but primarily I work with large organisations to help them, and their teams, write and manage large-scale websites. My focus in on scalability and performance, ensuring that front-end development projects can grow at a sustainable rate, while also remaining as fast as possible for the end user.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nAlthough my clients are very much international, Leeds is where I&rsquo;m based. I&rsquo;ve been here for just over nine years now and show no sign of leaving anytime soon; when I&rsquo;m not travelling for work, I can be found booting around West Yorkshire on either of my bikes or eating and drinking everything that this beautiful city can offer me.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;What initially sparked your interest in pursuing a career in technology?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;You know, it was a complete accident. I&rsquo;m not from a very technological family at all&mdash;the opposite, in fact! I didn&rsquo;t get internet access at home until I was 15 (2005) and my family all shared the one computer. I started off wanting to be a graphic designer and spent a lot of the time from 15 to 16, along with my then-best friend, Sam, working on logos and flyers and business cards for local businesses. After a good run at that, I decided that we needed a portfolio site to showcase our skills (we had no skills&mdash;looking back on it, the work was pretty weak), and volunteered myself to learn how to write HTML and CSS to build it.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Not long after starting that, I realised that not only did I much prefer coding, I was much, much better at it. A series of self-initiated projects later, and I was pretty convinced that this was what I wanted to do full-time. At 17, I began applying for front-end development jobs in Leeds and was picked up by&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/tonyjacobsleeds/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tony Jacobs, the Creative Director&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;at now-defunct Sense Internet. It&rsquo;s all gone on from there.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;You have worked with a number of leading tech organisations. What attracts you to a company?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;It&rsquo;s a complete mixture of things, but I&rsquo;ll be brutally honest and admit that one of them is vanity: as a self-employed developer, having prominent companies on my client list is a real boon.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nBut, of course, there are plenty of much better reasons. My background is in large-scale product environments&mdash;I spent around three years as a Senior Developer at Sky, in Leeds&mdash;so I have a skill-set that these companies value. I guess I&rsquo;m just a little more naturally inclined to that kind of environment.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nAlso, the problems that these companies face&mdash;famous or otherwise&mdash;present a fascinating challenge for me. The proposition, the pressure, and the obstacles posed are a great chance to tackle something new.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nFinally, I guess that if you&rsquo;re working for a well-known company, your work is likely to impact a far higher number of people. It&rsquo;s quite cool to see an advert for Trainline and knowing that I was the person responsible for making that site faster.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;You&rsquo;re a Google Developer Expert. Can you tell us more about what it means to be a Google Developer Expert and how you got to that level?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;I am! It&rsquo;s a great honour.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nA&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://developers.google.com/experts/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Google Developer Expert&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is an invited, non-Google developer who Google deem to be outstanding in their field. As well as technical abilities, they look for people who are good ambassadors within the tech community, who share and evangelise.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nTechnically, anyone can get there. If you&rsquo;re a great advocate and work hard to share knowledge in your field (mine is Technology, but the others are Marketing and Product Design), then a Google employee can invite you onto the program. Once they have made the invite, you then have to go through an interview process; first with an external Expert from the relevant area, and later an interview with a member Google staff.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nIf you pass those, then you&rsquo;re in! You&rsquo;re a GDE.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;img glober=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/File.ashx?path=Root/Images/8899794454_6800d9c2d1_z.jpg&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;You were also named Young Developer of the Year by&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.creativebloq.com/net-magazine&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Net Magazine&lt;/a&gt;. That&rsquo;s quite an achievement! What work were you doing at this time to be awarded such recognition?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hah! I was. That was a few years ago now, but it&rsquo;s true.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nAt the time, a lot of things had been happening in my career&mdash;I was beginning to speak at conferences with increasing frequency, I was writing a lot more articles, I was contributing to the open source space, and I&rsquo;d just started working for myself. It was a busy period for me, and I think that gave me prominence.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;What would be your advice to young developers hoping to make an impact in the technology sector?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/csswizardry/status/927183442130894848&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;I tweeted something recently&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;which seems to have resonated with a lot of people&mdash;entering tech now seems a lot more intimidating than it was for me a decade ago!&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nMy honest advice would be pace yourself, learn the fundamentals, and focus on integrity and resilience. There are lots and lots of new, shiny, exciting tools available, and more and more are appearing each week. While this does add an element of excitement, it also brings a lot a lot of fickleness, and what I see more and more is an entire generation of developers who&rsquo;re focusing on tools but neglecting the basics. Tooling, languages, and frameworks can be learned relatively quickly, but the fundamentals will never change; optimise for a stable baseline of understanding and then complement that with the specifics as and when you need them. That&rsquo;s a recipe for a much more robust and long-lasting career in tech, in my opinion.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;div class=&quot;SandboxRoot env-bp-350&quot; data-twitter-event-id=&quot;0&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;display: block; max-height: 10000px; direction: ltr; text-align: left; background: 0px 0px; font: 16px / 1.4 Helvetica, Roboto, &quot; ui=&quot;&quot;&gt;\n&lt;div class=&quot;EmbeddedTweet EmbeddedTweet--cta js-clickToOpenTarget&quot; data-click-to-open-target=&quot;https://twitter.com/csswizardry/status/927183442130894848&quot; data-iframe-title=&quot;Twitter Tweet&quot; data-scribe=&quot;page:tweet&quot; data-twitter-event-id=&quot;1&quot; id=&quot;twitter-widget-0&quot; lang=&quot;en&quot; style=&quot;overflow: hidden; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: 1px solid rgb(225, 232, 237); border-radius: 5px; max-widt