(13, 'Infographic - Top skills to succeed in DevOps', NULL, '', '', '9e2b9e70c779106eb7c9a68607e7beba.png', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/devops-jobs&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;DevOps&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is one of the biggest buzzwords in IT / software development right now, and it&rsquo;s only expected to get bigger. As companies work smarter and introduce new technology, they&rsquo;re increasingly looking for people who can enhance their technical capacities and drive development efficiencies in the process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;But what skills do you need to succeed in the world of DevOps?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;We published a blog on the top skills you need to succeed in DevOps (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/blogs/top-skills-you-need-to-succeed-in-devops-62092717261&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;read it here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;). Scroll below to view our infographic..&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Top skills to succeed in DevOps&quot; src=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/news/infographic-top-skills-to-succeed-in-devops-62163843399&quot; /&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/File.ashx?path=Root/Images/Amsource-topskills.png&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Top skills to succeed in DevOps [Infographic] by the team at &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/File.ashx?path=Root/Images/Amsource-topskills.png&quot;&gt;Amsource Technology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 1, '', 'DevOps', '', 'infographic-top-skills-to-succeed-in-devops', 'yes', 'yes', 1586867206),
(14, 'A Q&amp;A with Tanja Lichtensteiger of Sky Betting &amp; Gaming', 0, '', '', 'b6965cbcbd5fc10f5a0aae5379447cda.png', '&lt;h2 glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;In this Q&amp;A we hear from Tanja Lichtensteiger, Engineering Manager at&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://skybetcareers.com/about-us&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Sky Betting and Gaming&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;in Leeds!&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nTanja started coding at 8 years old and now, over two decades on, works as Engineering Manager for Sky Betting &amp; Gaming, managing and leading Software Development squads.&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;With 17 years&rsquo; experience of building systems under her belt, she believes in Tech&rsquo;s positive impact on people&rsquo;s lives and our futures. She has also been presented the Team Leader Award at the 2018&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.everywoman.com/events-awards/2018-FDM-everywoman-Technology-Awards&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;FDM Everywoman in Technology Awards&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and has been added to the&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.northernpowerwomen.com/portfolio/tanja-lichtensteiger/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Northern Power Women Future List 2018&lt;/a&gt;. As a mixed-race woman, Tanja is passionate about addressing the lack of women and ethnic minorities in Tech and leadership roles.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nHere she tells us more about her career journey, being a leader and advocate for women in tech, achievements, challenges and provides some advice for aspiring tech professionals.&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;What initially prompted you to pursue a career in technology?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;I accidentally found myself playing around with Q-Basic in computing class when I was 8 years old and then started coding Lego Robots using C when I was 11. I didn&rsquo;t look back.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;What opportunities were available to you as a young aspiring tech professional?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;I was living in Switzerland and couldn&rsquo;t speak French, although I spoke German and English, so the only opportunity available to me when I first started out was the apprenticeship pathway as I couldn&rsquo;t go to Uni.&nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;iframe allow=&quot;autoplay; encrypted-media&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/1diLc7YWvXA&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;How do these differ to what are available today for young people?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Most of the pathways that exist now, existed then, but you had to work doubly harder at it to find the right opportunity. These days it&rsquo;s more accepting to be working in tech without a degree or by being self-taught and you aren&rsquo;t easily dismissed.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;As a female leader in technology, what key advice from your experience would you give to someone looking to become a successful software professional?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;A very good quote once shared to me was &ldquo;We are all smart here. Differentiate yourself by being kind.&rdquo; I believe this holds true in our industry, don&rsquo;t overlook your softer skills when you&rsquo;re so focused on your technical skills. I prefer to hire good human beings.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Throughout your career journey, what have been your biggest challenges and how did you overcome them?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;As a mixed-race woman I had to deal with racism and sexism very early on in my career 17 years ago. Downright stubbornness and self-belief in my ability and that I belonged in tech made me resilient and I persisted.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;What has been your biggest achievement in your career to date?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;I can&rsquo;t think of one, I&rsquo;m just proud that when I look back on my journey I can see how people in my teams have grown to be good human beings as well as excellent technology professionals. Yes, we delivered some amazing solutions, but it really is all about the people and my contribution in shaping them as teams and individuals.&nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;You&rsquo;re an advocate for Women In Technology and work hard in both your work and spare time to raise the profile of Women in Tech. Are there any initiatives in particular at the moment you find most inspiring, that you feel are making a real difference for Women in Tech?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;em glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;I believe programmes such as&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.codefirstgirls.org.uk/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Code First: Girls&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;are absolutely vital. It gets girls, not just in to Computer Science degrees, to get hands on experience coding while being mentored by experienced and passionate techies, who are all volunteers and supporting this during their spare time. They finish the programmes with new technical skills and a fantastic supportive network. I have seen a positive impact from this activity in our local tech communities and long may it prosper!&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;twitter-widget class=&quot;twitter-tweet twitter-tweet-rendered&quot; data-tweet-id=&quot;994473288138149888&quot; id=&quot;twitter-widget-0&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border