(21, 'LDF Awards: Nominations Now Open!', 0, '', '', '67c4df38fe65cb0c17c0c2752e6eff45.png', '&lt;h2&gt;We&#039;re extremely excited to announce that we are teaming up with Ward Hadaway and Leeds Digital Festival yet again to bring you the second Leeds Digital Festival Awards!&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Last year the LDF Awards were the cherry on top of another fantastic&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://leedsdigitalfestival.org/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Leeds Digital Festival&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;which last year saw 160 events involving 400 companies, 600 speakers and a whopping 20,000 attendees!&nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\nOver the course of the&nbsp;two-week long&nbsp;festival, Leeds hosted more tech events than the tech capital of the world - San Francisco!&lt;br /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;What are the awards all about?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nThe Leeds Digital Festival Awards celebrate all that is great about the digital &amp; tech industry in Leeds and the wider city region in the last year. The thriving scene is home to start-ups, SME&rsquo;s and larger businesses where tech is at the heart of everything they do.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\nThe awards celebrate the organisations and individuals driving the vibrant industry.&nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\nThe awards are an opportunity for the people of Leeds to have their&nbsp;say,&nbsp;and celebrate the people and organisations they believe deserve some recognition for their contribution to the digital sector, in our city over the last 12 months.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Catch footage from last year&rsquo;s awards here&hellip;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;iframe allow=&quot;accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/s-3UnExGLQQ&quot; width=&quot;560&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://leedsdigitalfestivalawards.org/awards&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;What categories are up for nomination?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Entrepreneur of the Year (sponsored by&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://little.agency/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Little&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nFor the business leader who inspires innovation with the drive to make ideas become a reality, driving their team to success&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;2018 winner:&lt;/b&gt;&nbsp;ALEX CRAVEN&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Facilitator of the Year (sponsored by&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.leeds.ac.uk/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&nbsp;University of Leeds&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nThis award recognises individuals, tech hubs, incubators, universities, co-working spaces, events or other organisations that support the tech and digital ecosystem in Leeds and the wider city region&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;2018 winner:&lt;/b&gt;&nbsp;ODI LEEDS&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;One to Watch 2019 (sponsored by&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://brownshipley.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Brown Shipley&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nFor the team player with big ambitions who goes above and beyond to do themselves, their team and their company proud.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;2018 winner:&lt;/b&gt;&nbsp;HANNEKA KILBURN&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Start-up of the Year (sponsored by&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://wizuworkspace.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Wizu&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nThis award celebrates the hard work and success of tech and digital start-ups in Leeds and the city region who have shown the best innovations and/or company growth. Nominated companies will be incorporated no later than Jan 2017.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;2018 winner:&nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;SYNAP&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Growth Company of the Year ( sponsored&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.sedulo.co.uk/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Sedulo&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nThe award for the tech business showing the most growth in the last 12 months through their success, driving increases in headcount&nbsp;and / or&nbsp;turnover.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&nbsp;This award is&nbsp;brand&nbsp;new addition for 2019!&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Tech Innovation of the Year (Sponored&nbsp;by&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.crispthinking.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Crisp&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nThe award for&nbsp;ground breaking&nbsp;research or project that pushes the possibility in tech and digital.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;2018 winner:&lt;/b&gt;&nbsp;HARK SYSTEMS&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Tech4Good (sponsored by&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.leeds.gov.uk/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Leeds City Council&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nThe person, organisation or technology that is delivering positive change within communities or the environment and making the world a better place.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&nbsp;This award is&nbsp;brand&nbsp;new addition for 2019!&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Tech Employer of the Year (sponsored by&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bjss.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;BJSS&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nThe company doing the most for&nbsp;their&nbsp;employees through training, development and innovative working practices in the tech / digital community.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&nbsp;This award is&nbsp;brand&nbsp;new addition for 2019!&lt;br /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;How do I place my nominations?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://leedsdigitalfestivalawards.org/nominate&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;CLICK HERE TO PLACE YOUR NOMINATIONS TODAY!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;Who are the judges?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\nThe final shortlisted nominees will be judged by a panel of familiar figures in the Leeds digital and business sectors. Including Chelsea Hardy of&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nexusleeds.co.uk/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Nexus&lt;/a&gt;, Deb Hetherington of&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.leedsbeckett.ac.uk/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Leeds Beckett University&lt;/a&gt;,&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/&quot;&gt;Yorkshire Post&lt;/a&gt;&rsquo;s Greg Wright, 2018&rsquo;s winner of Entrepreneur of the year Alex Craven as well as awards sponsors Andrew&nbsp;Maeer&nbsp;of Amsource Technology and Gareth Yates of Ward Hadaway.&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;br /&gt;\n&lt;b&gt;Click here to meet the judges...&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://leedsdigitalfestivalawards.org/judges&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/File.ashx?path=Root/Images/1.0_Amsource_Leeds_Digital_Festival_2019_meet_the_judges.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;Entries will close on Friday 22nd March!&nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;', '', 1, '', '', '', 'ldf-awards-nominations-now-open-', 'yes', 'no', 1550534400),
(22, 'Infographic: How can Social Media help your job search?', NULL, '', '', '367b64940e35e43d2761a50313f9ef10.png', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;Professionals searching for a job these days are spoilt for choice with the amount of search outlets they can use to find one. Before technology had adapted to the stage it is at now, those searching for a job were limited to the ways they could interact with employers. Nowadays there are so many ways candidates can interact with companies and employers to help secure the job they are looking for.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;This infographic provides some advice to job seekers on how to use social media to maximise their job search. (Read more&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/blogs/the-social-job-search-have-you-started-yours--51971610493&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;How Social Media can be used in your Job search&quot; src=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/File.ashx?path=Root/Images/1.1SOCIAL_MEDIA_JOB_SEARCH_INFOGRAPHIC.jpghttps://www.amsourcetechnology.com/news/infographic-how-can-social-media-help-your-job-search--61951311173&quot; /&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/news/infographic-how-can-social-media-help-your-job-search--61951311173&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;How Social Media can be used in your Job search [Infographic] by the team at &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/news/infographic-how-can-social-media-help-your-job-search--61951311173&quot;&gt;Amsource Technology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 1, '', '', '', 'infographic-how-can-social-media-help-your-job-search-', 'yes', 'yes', 1586868435),
(23, 'Avoid these Interview Nightmares!', 0, '', '', '89939ed7809a21984e98e664e8473222.png', '&lt;h2 glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Leaving an interview knowing that you have not performed to the best of your ability is not a good feeling.&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;There&#039;s no reason to have an interview nightmare. Make sure you know how to avoid these common mistakes...&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Not knowing about the role&hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;428&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/jquDWJfPUMCiI&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Prepare for an interview by finding out all that you possibly can about the role you&rsquo;re applying for.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nThere&rsquo;s nothing worse for hiring managers than being presented with a candidate at interview stage who clearly has no idea about the role they&rsquo;re applying for.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Study the job spec. If you&rsquo;re unsure about anything don&rsquo;t be afraid to ask your recruiter. Any decent&nbsp; recruiter will&nbsp; know the roles they hire for inside out, so will be happy to help you out and advise you accordingly.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Not knowing about the company&hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;480&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/51Uiuy5QBZNkoF3b2Z&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;A common, detrimental error a lot of candidates still make is to not research the company.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nThese days candidates are spoilt for choice with outlets they are able to find out information about the companies they are interviewing for.&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;So there&#039;s no excuse, do your research.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Find out the company&rsquo;s history, milestones, values, services and who their customers are. As well as paying attention to the company&rsquo;s presence over social media such as Twitter, LinkedIn and Facebook. What have they been up to? What blog posts have the posted recently? Impress your interviewer with just how much you know about their company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;By doing your research it will also give you a better stance on how much you actually want to work for the company. You may do your research and realise that the company isn&rsquo;t for you, or you may find it makes you more excited and determined for a potential future with the organisation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Not knowing why you want the job - show enthusiasm&hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;270&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/xT1XGWbE0XiBDX2T8Q&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Taking the previous points into consideration will help you find the answer to &lsquo;why you want the job&rsquo;.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\nA lack of enthusiasm is a real turn off for employers. Why would you want to employ someone who lacks enthusiasm, and doesn&rsquo;t even know why they want the job?&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;If you really want the job and the interviewer asks you &#039;why?&#039;,&nbsp; you need to be prepared to give an answer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;This also comes hand in hand with body language. Try not to use closed body gestures, this creates the impression that you&rsquo;re closed off.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Not explaining, how!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;270&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/l0MYL06eQHNda2tR6&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;So, on your CV you will have stated that you possess certain skills. A lot of the time your interviewer will need a lot more convincing than the writing on the paper to be in confidence that you do in fact have the skills and attributes you say you do.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;For every skill you state, have a story that demonstrates a time you have achieved the results you wanted, down to these skills and attributes you have. Be prepared to talk about these.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Badmouthing previous employers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; height=&quot;411&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/3t7RAFhu75Wwg&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot; width=&quot;480&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;You may have had some unpleasant experiences in previous working environments. It&#039;s important not to delve into the nitty gritty of why your experience was particularly bad, especially if it puts you at risk of bad mouthing your previous colleagues, or talking about how much you hated your boss. This has the potential to show you in a negative light, so avoid where possible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Not asking questions&hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;360&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/jUwpNzg9IcyrK&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;At the end of an interview, there will be the option for the candidate to ask the interviewer questions. Whilst we say, &lsquo;the option&rsquo;, there really isn&rsquo;t an option but to ask questions.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Not asking any questions displays to the interviewer a lack of interest from the candidate&rsquo;s side. So it&rsquo;s really important to ask questions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Examples of things you could ask questions about include: progression, company culture, or upcoming projects. Avoid questions about salary and benefits (especially at first stage interview).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Obviously if you plan to ask questions and then the interviewer actually answers all the questions you had before you ask, let them know this, and maybe give examples of the questions you were going to ask.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Not following up&hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;270&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/3o6ZtctTqhjH5H7pv2&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Don&rsquo;t be afraid to follow up after an interview.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;The people who are interviewing you are busy people, therefore it may take them a while at times to give feedback. By grabbing the bull by the horns and emailing and ringing to ask for feedback it shows that you are pro-active, and ultimately, that you are interested in the role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Forgetting the basics&hellip;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;360&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/l0CLVr9NHLoqVtICQ&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Punctuality &ndash;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Don&rsquo;t be late. Know where it is you have to be and make sure you get there, account for any problems that you may encounter on your way and make time for that. Lateness is always a no no. However sometimes, things do happen which may result in you being late, if it looks like you may be late, let your interviewer know as soon as possible.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Dress code -&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;dress in a professional manner. Be clear of the dress code before the interview.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Be professional -&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Be yourself. But keep in mind you are in a professional environment so ensure that you try to keep the slang you may use with your friends at a minimum.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;h2 glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 20px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Don&#039;t dwell on your mistakes...&lt;/h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot; class=&quot;giphy-embed&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; glober=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;271&quot; src=&quot;https://giphy.com/embed/G4rIGiMVtrJ1S&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Mistakes do happen, after all we&#039;re only human. Probably the most detrimental of mistakes to make would be to give up after having made an interview mistake or being rejected from a role. Ask for feedback from your recruiter and understand what went wrong, work on it, move on and try again! You will gain confidence with every interview you take part in, which will allow you to be better each time.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Keep these points in mind when preparing for an interview and see if they help you. Have you had an interview nightmare? How did you overcome it, tweet us&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://twitter.com/AmsourceTech&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;@AmsourceTech&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Read more careers advice blogs&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/posts/tags-careers-advice&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 1, '', '', '', 'avoid-these-interview-nightmares-', 'yes', 'no', 1540857600),
(24, 'Infographic - The Digital Northern Powerhouse', NULL, '', '', 'f01d1e28e2e3d89c042c279cfa405fdb.png', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;The North is gradually becoming widely recognised as a center for digital excellence in the UK, with more and more tech professionals now choosing the region as a base for their careers and boosting the government backed ideology of a &#039;Northern Powerhouse&#039;. (See our previous infographic&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/blogs/technology-in-the-uk-53221810563&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;The North is home to a number of leading technology clusters, the area is thriving in expertise from games tech, health tech, e-commerce to software development with a vibrant start-up scene the region over.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;In our latest infographic we use research from&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.techcityuk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Tech-Nation-2016_FINAL-ONLINE-1.pdf&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(34, 61, 117); text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tech City&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot;Glober W01&quot;, arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to take a look at the key locations in The North driving this Digital Northern powerhouse...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;img src=&#039;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/File.ashx?path=Root/Images/2211Dig_northern_power_infograph.jpg&#039; width=&#039;540&#039; alt=&#039;The Digital Northern Powerhouse&#039;&#039;&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&#039;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/news/infographic-the-digital-northern-powerhouse-61061593726&#039;&gt;\r\n&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Digital Northern Powerhouse [Infographic] by the team at &lt;a href=&#039;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/news/infographic-the-digital-northern-powerhouse-61061593726&#039;&gt;Amsource Technology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/a&gt;', '', 1, '', '', '', 'infographic-the-digital-northern-powerhouse', 'yes', 'yes', 1586868763);
