(5, 'Amsource Visits Leeds Digital Job Fair', 0, '', '', '3678dbd613ca227511c8171a949376b0.png', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;With the digital economy in the UK thriving, it&rsquo;s definitely an exciting time to be a tech professional.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;In a recent report by Tech city&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.techcityuk.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&ldquo;Tech Nation 2016: Transforming UK Industries&rdquo;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;it was recorded that turnover growth in the UK&rsquo;s Digital technology industries grew 32% faster than the rest of the economy in 2010-2014.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;On Wednesday we went along to the&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://herd.careers/jobfair/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Leeds Digital Job Fair&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;at the&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.firstdirectarena.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;First Direct arena&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;. The event was the first of its kind in Leeds with the aim to bring together the future of digital talent in Leeds.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Leeds digital jobs fair to bridge the skills gap?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;It was reported by the&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.yorkshirepost.co.uk/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Yorkshire Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;the worrying evidence that many technology firms are struggling with a digital skills gap, who are experiencing difficulty finding the right candidates with the right skills. Women in tech is also a pressing issue in the tech industry with a significant gender gap being felt in the majority of technology companies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://twitter.com/tweetvanbar/status/697017096341946368&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Amy De-Balsi, founder of Leeds online job board&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://herd.careers/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;HERD&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;, stated that the number of vacancies in the Leeds digital sector has risen by almost half over the last 12 months from 400 roles to 600 roles. However with a lack of candidates with the correct skills, more needs to be done to get more people into technology based careers. Therefore the Leeds digital job fair was a perfect opportunity to make head way in doing this.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;More than 30 technology businesses including&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.skybet.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Sky Bet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;,&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.providentfinancial.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Provident Financial,&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.bjss.com/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;BJSS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.pg.com/en_UK/&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Proctor and Gamble&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;came along to showcase their businesses and hundreds of vacancies to around 2,000 prospective technology candidates. It was really great to see the turnout of attendees and the sheer number of exciting technology companies looking to support the growth of the digital economy in the North.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;strong glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Why a digital focus on Leeds and The North?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;While the focus for technology professionals for where they base their careers has typically always been in London, it seems recently there has been a significant shift of techies moving to other technology clusters across the UK, including those in Cambridge, Bath and Bristol but in particular those in the North of England (Leeds, Manchester and Sheffield), driving the much talked about&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/business/innovation/digital-sector-beating-heart-northern-10128148&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Northern Powerhouse&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;. (See our info-graphic&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/blogs/technology-in-the-uk-53221810563&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;)&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;We recently wrote a&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://www.amsourcetechnology.com/news/leeds-experiences-strongest-salary-growth-in-2015-61313121441&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;about how Leeds workers were more likely to receive a pay rise in 2015, and&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a glober=&quot;&quot; href=&quot;https://twitter.com/TechCityUK/status/697688727997571072&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Tech City&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;research has found that salaries for Leeds technology workers have increased by 29% between 2012 and 2015. Stats found in our infographic state that out of 47,000 companies founded since 2013, 50% were digital and 74% were based outside of London, demonstrating the evident shift of talent from the capital, providing food for thought for aspiring tech professionals in the UK in terms of where to base their careers in the future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;br glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot; /&gt;\n&lt;span glober=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 65, 122); font-family: &quot; w01=&quot;&quot;&gt;Throughout our visit to the job fair we took the opportunity to have a chat with some of the companies in attendance and to hear their thoughts on the digital economy in Yorkshire and the attraction of tech professionals to The North.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;div class=&quot;SandboxRoot env-bp-350&quot; data-twitter-event-id=&quot;0&quot; segoe=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;display: block; max-height: 10000px; direction: ltr; 