(41, 'page', 'c_suite', 'c-suite-desc', '', 'When firms scale up, it&rsquo;s all-too-common to see ambitious plans derailed by skill deficits. Our C-suite advisory will keep you on track by building a talent pipeline that&rsquo;s aligned with your evolving needs. With unrivalled insight into the tech talent pool, we can provide up-to-the-minute salary benchmarking, and create talent maps to optimise operational agility. Or design an engagement strategy that gives you a vital edge in the battle to recruit and retain top talent.', 'textarea', 'youtube', NULL, NULL, 2, 1583405343),
