(6, 4, 'Generic Testimonial 2', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Is et unt, te plaut remoloriosa nam, comnitatur, seque di cuptatae. Ut odiam desto volectis etur? Ed quatia volupta spitibu sandios dit officto eumquam as magnam, volo ventendi torumquiati inturion nis apient et ommolore nim seque imusdae. Nemos eati ommolo tet dolenim eniandit lant quate cusapitium eos eum eumquod itiur, officiandit la por apiet faceat et quo odi tem et fuga. Net ilit as et voluptaqui beatur sitior maiorpo reicipis natur maximai orenis molupti blatur, quaepudae dolorrores et vid et ullaut voloribus, ut alis nis nam soluptatur aut volorit, ut andigenihil et int.&lt;/p&gt;', 'no'),
(7, 5, 'Careers at BJSS', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;Our people are what set us apart. We recruit and develop outstanding people in a culture where they can excel and collaborate with like-minded colleagues to deliver the high-quality outcomes our clients expect from us.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We want our people to make the most of their talent and potential, so we&rsquo;re committed to supporting their personal and professional development. Our reputation for excellence means we can provide exciting career development opportunities working on rewarding engagements for some of the world&rsquo;s leading organisations.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', 'no'),
(8, 5, 'What Makes Us Different', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;We&rsquo;re not your typical consultancy. You won&rsquo;t find a strict hierarchy or a constrained career path. Your Squad Lead has a pastoral role and is responsible for ensuring that you have a great employee experience, and most importantly works with you to determine the course of your career at BJSS.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We attract the best in the business, meaning that you have the opportunity to work alongside some of the most talented people in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We don&rsquo;t believe in information siloes so we don&rsquo;t have traditional departments. Instead, we have communities of practice that ensure quality in our work. We encourage you to join other capabilities that are of interest and enhance your personal growth.&lt;/p&gt;', 'no'),
(9, 6, 'Phil - Software Engineer, Zen Internet', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;No two days are the same at Zen; one day you could be working on a new page for a website and the next you could be learning new, interesting technologies or you could be meeting with customers to get feedback. It&rsquo;s a great place to work as you are able to explore new ideas and technologies, you are encouraged to learn and grow as a coder and you are given the time you need to deliver quality code.&lt;/p&gt;', 'no'),
(10, 7, 'Trevor', '', 'ea2987a50ca690bccafea5e0b1f948e9.jpg', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;b id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-c81afd2b-7fff-83f7-0875-5ec38bbcf98a&quot;&gt;Tartan Yachts offer an unparalleled experience sailing the world. Knowing we are building not only a best-in-class sailboat, but a lifestyle, is something to be proud of.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'no'),
(11, 7, 'Cole', '', '9b165efaeaacc81c9b25f4cce4e4cee9.jpg', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;b id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-7601a9cb-7fff-b965-ed95-1aaec9928711&quot;&gt;I&rsquo;ve been with Tartan for years and take pride in the craftsmanship behind our sailboats. The entire manufacturing process is carefully engineered for perfection.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'no'),
(12, 7, 'Bennett', '', 'bf8d8c7972a1b6893fd0935dd10b9422.jpg', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;b id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-efcead61-7fff-6445-53ce-989c668c60d3&quot;&gt;Culture at Tartan is like a family. We are building together, literally, and growing together. I feel at home.&nbsp; &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'no'),
