(24, 'Software Project Manager', 'SPMUSA', 'permanent', '$80k - $110k', '&lt;p&gt;As a Project Manager you will be responsible for a combination of managing the client side implementation of different products to multiple customers, whilst co-ordinating internal teams/resources to ensure this is completed efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Customer stakeholders will vary to include Senior level Directors, along with their technology team.&nbsp; Internally, you will work closely with the sales, professional services and technology teams to drive efficiency in the delivery and implementation of the products.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Whilst already a market leading organization boasting some of the largest automotive and supply chain businesses in the world on their client roster, a period of change is being undertaken to modernize.&nbsp; This is a great time to join to have the opportunity to contribute to the future in the way the organization operates, with significant opportunity to influence operations in the US.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;To be successful in this role, you will have the following experience:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Proven previous experience of managing software development projects&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Proven previous experience of delivering customized SaaS products&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Any experience of major vendor technology beneficial (e.g. NetSuite, Oracle, PeopleSoft, Salesforce, SAP, Lawson, JD Edwards, Microsoft Dynamics or Workday)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Experience of ERP, Fleet, Asset or Supply Chain Management solutions beneficial&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Technical knowledge around Cloud tech (Azure/AWS)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The office base for this role is Central Massachusetts but can be predominantly home based with travel to customer sites when required.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Flexibility in working hours will be required to co-ordinate with a globally based team.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary is flexible for this role, $80-110,000.&nbsp; Candidates looking for $100-110,000 will be required to show experience in a lead role, co-ordinating the work of other Project Managers as part of an implementation team.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; margin-right:0cm; margin-left:0cm&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; margin-right:0cm; margin-left:0cm&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;This role is working for an industry leading SaaS software product organization, and is a key part of their customer implementation team.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 22, '|13||11|', 'software-project-manager', 'yes', 'yes', 674, '', 1631567895, 1590969600),
(25, 'DevOps Engineer', 'DOEL', 'permanent', 'Up to &pound;50k', '&lt;p&gt;My client is&nbsp;building a brand new tech hub and as a result; are looking to hire DevOps Engineers.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They will be building a brand new, cloud first, platform which is fundamental to how the company runs. The platform hasn&rsquo;t even launched yet, so you will be instrumental in getting it ready for launch later this year.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will get to work with the latest Cloud / Microservices technologies including Terraform, Lambda and AWS. As a DevOps Engineer you will deploy and maintain scalable, highly available application solutions that leverage AWS services.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They have a great environment and emphasis on training and progression of staff. They&rsquo;re egoless and value everyone&rsquo;s input. The Technical Lead directly quoted &ldquo;if someone comes in with an idea and they can prove the value, we&rsquo;ll do it&rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This is a rare opportunity as you will be working with zero technical debt, you will be building a best in class system from scratch.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key experience required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;AWS&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Terraform or CloudFormation&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Puppet, Chef or Ansible&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Scripting with either Bash, Python, Ruby etc&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;CI / CD&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0cm 0cm 8pt&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0cm 0cm 8pt&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are currently working with a household name who are new to the Leeds tech market.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 13, '|11||15||16|', 'devops-engineer', 'yes', 'no', 0, '', 1631567895, 1591747200),
(26, 'Senior Product Owner', 'AM34358', 'permanent', '&pound;60-80,000', '&lt;p&gt;Calling ambitious Senior level Product Owners - this is an opportunity to shape the future of a market leading FinTech currently undertaking rapid growth following significant investment.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will join a team in a lead capacity on a major SaaS replatforming programme whilst also maintaining legacy products.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be an expert at crafting user stories, working with the development team to build products that deliver value rapidly.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You understand the need and aren&#039;t afraid to ask difficult questions, all the time asking what value will that deliver. You understand and are experienced aligning business strategy to technology solutions, and the need to balance technical produces with commercial reality.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be an Agile expert.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will work with the Head of Product to shape the team, mentoring other PO&#039;s/BA&#039;s.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;An excellent salary is available - &pound;60-80k + up to 50% bonus&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Calling ambitious Senior level Product Owners - this is an opportunity to shape the future of a market leading FinTech currently undertaking rapid growth following significant investment.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '50% Bonus', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 22, '|17|', 'senior-product-owner', 'yes', 'yes', 211, '', 1631567895, 1592784000),
(27, 'Implementation Project Manager', 'JM', 'permanent', '$80-100,000', '&lt;p&gt;This role is working for an industry leading SaaS software product organization, and is a key part of their customer implementation team.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As a Project Manager you will be responsible for a combination of managing the client side implementation of different products to multiple customers, whilst co-ordinating internal teams/resources to ensure this is completed efficiently.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Customer stakeholders will vary to include Senior level Directors, along with their technology team.&nbsp;Internally, you will work closely with the sales, professional services and technology teams to drive efficiency in the delivery and implementation of the products.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Whilst already a market leading organization boasting some of the largest automotive and supply chain businesses in the world on their client roster, a period of change is being undertaken to modernize.&nbsp;This is a great time to join to have the opportunity to contribute to the future in the way the organization operates, with significant opportunity to influence operations in the US.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;To be successful in this role, you will have the following experience:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Proven previous experience of managing SaaS software projects&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Proven previous experience of delivering customized SaaS products&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Any experience of major vendor technology beneficial (e.g. NetSuite, Oracle, PeopleSoft, Salesforce, SAP, Lawson, JD Edwards, Microsoft Dynamics or Workday)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Experience of ERP, Fleet, Asset or Supply Chain Management solutions beneficial&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Proven experience of various project sizes, $300k - $3m ideally&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The office base for this role is Central Massachusetts but can be predominantly home based with travel to customer sites when required.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Flexibility in working hours will be required to co-ordinate with a globally based team.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Join a new team implementing a market leading SaaS products into Fortune500 clients and SMEs.&nbsp; Home based/remote role working with a global team.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '+ Benefits', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 22, '|6||13||17|', 'implementation-project-manager', 'yes', 'yes', 473, '', 1631567895, 1593043200),
(28, 'Implementation Consultant', 'JM1', 'permanent', '$80-100,000', '&lt;p&gt;This role is working for an industry leading SaaS software product organization, and is a key part of their customer implementation team.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Implementation Consultants are responsible for working with customers to configure and integrate this market leading SaaS product suite into a complex enterprise environment.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Customer stakeholders will vary to include Senior level Directors, along with their technology team.&nbsp;Internally, you will work closely with the sales, professional services and technology teams to drive efficiency in the delivery and implementation of the products.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Whilst already a market leading organization boasting some of the largest automotive and supply chain businesses in the world on their client roster, a period of change is being undertaken to modernize.&nbsp;This is a great time to join to have the opportunity to contribute to the future in the way the organization operates, with significant opportunity to influence operations in the US.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;To be successful in this role, you will have the following experience:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Proven previous experience of implementing SaaS products&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Proven previous experience of delivering customized SaaS products&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Experience of major vendors technology beneficial (e.g. NetSuite, Oracle, PeopleSoft, Salesforce, SAP, Lawson, JD Edwards, Microsoft Dynamics or Workday)&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Experience of ERP, Fleet, Asset or Supply Chain Management solutions highly beneficial&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Strong technical integration skills with SQL (any ETL highly desirable)&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Web skills with HTML/CSS&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This role can be home based with travel to customer sites with the office base in Central Mass.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Flexibility in working hours will be required to co-ordinate with a globally based team.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Join a team implementing a market leading product among some of America&#039;s well known brand organizations.&nbsp; Remote/Home based in a global team.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '+ Benefits', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 22, '|6||13||17|', 'implementation-consultant', 'yes', 'yes', 506, '', 1631567895, 1593043200),
(3059, 'CTO', 'MD34377', 'permanent', 'Negotiable', '&lt;p&gt;This opportunity is to help bring an already proven idea to Europe, partnering with some of the world&rsquo;s leading communications companies. Everything is in place for mass adoption of this product, they now need you to help them do this.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Having already built the MvP, investment into the business has been made for a greenfield development of the flagship product. Partnerships are in place for the development of the product and for when it has been delivered, work needs to start asap.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;About you:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be a software engineer at heart, likely been a tech lead, manager and possibly now a head of engineering looking to step up to CTO.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Experience of leading development teams, managing product roadmaps and ensuring delivery is made on time.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will have an expert understand of how API&rsquo;s are built and how they integrate on an enterprise scale.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will have worked in at least one of these environments &ndash; Blockchain, Mobile or Peer to Peer&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Opportunity:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Joining at such an early stage means you will have a huge influence on the technology, product and shape of the whole business. Working closely with the CEO &amp; Founder to help implement his vision for the business.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Salary is open to negotiation and significant shares have been allocated to this role.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;My client is a well-funded start-up and are supported by one of the leading forces of future tech &ndash; AI/ Blockchain/ Robotics etc.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 9, '|19|', 'cto', 'yes', 'no', 536, '', 1631567895, 1593734400),
(3060, 'Product Director / CPO', 'MD34377', 'permanent', 'Negotiable', '&lt;p&gt;My client is a well-funded start-up and are supported by one of the leading forces of future tech &ndash; AI/ Blockchain/ Robotics etc.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This opportunity is to help bring an already proven idea to Europe, partnering with some of the world&rsquo;s leading communications companies. Everything is in place for mass adoption of this product, they now need you to help them do this.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Having already built the MvP, investment into the business has been made for a greenfield development of the flagship product. Partnerships are in place for the development of the product and for when it has been delivered, work needs to start asap.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;About you:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be a product expert, likely risen through the ranks of Product Owner and Product Manager, now looking for the step into strategic leadership as a Product Director/ Chief Product Officer.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Experience of working the development teams, managing product roadmaps and ensuring delivery is made on time.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will understand how API&rsquo;s are built and how they integrate on an enterprise scale.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will have worked in at least one of these environments &ndash; Blockchain, Mobile or Peer to Peer&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Opportunity:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Joining at such an early stage means you will have a huge influence on the product and shape of the whole business. Working closely with the CEO &amp; Founder and development partner to help implement his vision for the business.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Salary is open to negotiation and significant shares have been allocated to this role.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;This opportunity is to help bring an already proven idea to Europe, partnering with some of the world&rsquo;s leading communications companies.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 9, '|19|', 'product-director-cpo', 'yes', 'no', 561, '', 1631567895, 1593734400),
(3061, '.Net Developer', 'SL34397', 'permanent', '&euro;65k - with Share / Equity Options', '&lt;p&gt;You will be wholly responsible for the design and development of this key part of the application with the full support of the CTO. This module is critical to the mass adoption of the company&rsquo;s flagship product, which is disrupting and modernizing the German Healthcare market.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The final product will completely modernise the way in which the healthcare industry operates and facilitate the integration of millions of data sets. It will act as the central platform for future decades and generations for other healthcare systems and programmes to integrate in to and revolutionise doctor-patient interaction. There is no system like this in Germany and your efforts will significantly help revolutionize how healthcare systems are used.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Your opportunity will also include shares options, flexible and remote working, and future progression opportunity to lead teams and learn from a hands-on CTO.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This is a great opportunity to join an organisation that have received significant (&euro;m&rsquo;s) funding and have already grown to 20 people in 2 years. They will grow to more than 40 by the end of the year.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;For regulatory reasons, this person must be a minimum of B1 level German with fluent English-speaking ability.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Nice-To-Have Skills&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;.NET Core&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;SQL&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;XML/XSD/XSLT&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Data-Security and Data-Protection requirements&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I am recruiting an experienced C# Developer with strong Relational Database &amp; migration / ETL knowledge to lead the design and build of a brand new MedTech platform.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 20, '|6|', '-net-developer-sl34397', 'yes', 'yes', 195, '', 1631567895, 1593734400),
(3062, 'Lead Developer', 'CP34533', 'permanent', '&pound;55-65k', '&lt;p&gt;Utilising cutting edge technology such as AI and Machine Learning the company are pushing the boundaries of entire industry, that effects millions of people daily.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be working on real time mission critical systems,&nbsp;challenging the status quo, and making a real difference to the industry by creating new ways to solve real problems&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The company has won a host of awards including the prestigious Queens Award for Enterprise. Due to this they are growing year on year and are now looking to add a Lead C# Developer to the team.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As a lead you will work closely with the technical leadership team on a variety of projects.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will lead a team of developers and be responsible for key project and architectural decision making including providing insights into the latest technologies. As a lead C# Developer, you will get the opportunity to mentor junior members of the team and be directly involved with helping the team grow over time.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They are looking for a candidate with a strong background in C#, you will also get the opportunities to work with the latest cloud technologies such as AWS.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Skills and experience&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;C#&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;ASP.Net MVC&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Angular / React / VueJS&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;AWS / Azure&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Two or more years of development team leadership&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Experience of mentoring junior developers&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Any previous C++ experience would be advantageous for this role.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary for this position is paying between &pound;60-65k plus an annual bonus.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This is a great opportunity to challenge yourself, make your mark in a growing company and on the world, and be rewarded for it&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Please apply for a confidential discussion&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;The key member of the dev&nbsp;team, combining leadership with your technical expertise&nbsp;to make the team better and technology solutions superior.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', 'Bonus, Pension', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 25, '|6||11||7||17||24|', 'lead-developer', 'yes', 'yes', 390, '', 1631567895, 1594771200),
(3063, 'Test Enginner / QA Tester', 'JM34224', 'permanent', 'Up to &pound;35k', '&lt;p&gt;They have modernised their Yorkshire based HQ and turned it into their head R&amp;D centre, which means that all future growth, progression and projects will be located in this Yorkshire based tech hub.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They have grown significantly by acquiring their competition, which has strengthened their product portfolio. They are now going through a business and IT transformation where they are streamlining all their products and services and modernising their tech / how they deliver them to their customers. This includes Agile / DevOps principles and .Net Core.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they are a global business, they still have the feeling of a medium-sized business and are not corporate, maintaining a family-friendly working environment where work-life balance and employee wellbeing are key.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As a QA Tester you&nbsp;will work as part of a larger QA team and be responsible for ensuring that products meet the established standards of quality including reliability, usability, and performance. As well as it being important to provide tactful, insightful feedback to maintain a good working relationship with end users and other global product teams.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Ideally you will have some automation experience with Selenium and be keen to do more in this area (6-12 months+ experience).&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key Experience Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;2+ years QA / Testing experience&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Web/SaaS testing experience&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Automation - Selenium&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;JIRA/Test Rails&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;VS TFS.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Git&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;TeamCity&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They are offering an excellent benefits package and a salary up to around &pound;35,000 for this role.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are currently working with a Leeds based&nbsp;software house who operate globally across 4 continents.They are looking for a talent Test Engineer / QA Tester to join their team.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|6||21||24|', 'test-enginner-qa-tester', 'yes', 'yes', 234, '', 1631567895, 1594771200),
(3064, 'Senior Tester / Test Lead', 'JM34225', 'permanent', 'Up to &pound;45k', '&lt;p&gt;They have modernised their Yorkshire based HQ and turned it into their head R&amp;D centre, which means that all future growth, progression and projects will be located in this Yorkshire based tech hub.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They have grown significantly by acquiring their competition, which has strengthened their product portfolio. They are now going through a business and IT transformation where they are streamlining all their products and services and modernising their tech / how they deliver them to their customers. This includes Agile / DevOps principles and .Net Core.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they are a global business, they still have the feeling of a medium-sized business and are not corporate, maintaining a family-friendly working environment where work-life balance and employee wellbeing are key.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As the Test Lead you&nbsp;will be a key part of a larger QA team, being able to mentor and manage a team QA tester. You will also be responsible for ensuring that products meet the established standards of quality including reliability, usability, and performance. As well as it being important to provide tactful, insightful feedback to maintain a good working relationship with end users and other global product teams.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Ideally you will have technical skills, but if not in depth you will be the kind of person who will be proactive in their learning and development with a can-do, solution driven attitude.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key Experience Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Proven QA experience&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Some exposure to a technical testing discipline, such as automation testing.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Mentoring experience &ndash; 2-3 testers&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Experience/Exposure to Selenium&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;VS TFS&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They are offering an excellent bene