(3066, 'UX Designer', 'CP34531', 'permanent', '&pound;40-50k', '&lt;p&gt;The organisation already operated&nbsp;flexible and modern approach to working with 2 &ndash; 3 days remote pre-covid. Utilising cutting edge technology such as AI and Machine Learning the company are pushing the boundaries of entire industry, that effects millions of people daily.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be working on real time mission critical systems,&nbsp;challenging the status quo, and making a real difference to the industry by creating new ways to solve real problems&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The company has won a host of awards including the prestigious Queens Award for Enterprise. Due to this they are growing year on year and are now looking to add a UX designer to join the team.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As a UX Designer you will get the opportunity to make the role your own, they are looking for someone to take their award-winning product and make it something that is a joy to use.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Skills and Experience&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;3+ years plus &#039;UX&#039; Design experience as minimum.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Expereince conducting user research, competitor analysis and analysis data&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Good knowledge of user stories, personas, and storyboards.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Journey mapping. Information architecture. &ndash;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;To conduct usability testing.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Have worked on Desktop, App and Dynamic Web sites.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Created Wireframes&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Created Prototypes&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Excellent stakeholder management.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This is a great opportunity to challenge yourself, make your mark in a growing company and on the world, and be rewarded for it&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Salaries for this role range from &pound;40,000 - &pound;50,000&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Please apply for a confidential discussion&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;A remarkable opportunity that will provide the opportunity to establish and define the UX approach.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', 'Bonus, Pension', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 25, '|25||10||7||6|', 'ux-designer', 'yes', 'yes', 351, '', 1631567895, 1595289600),
(3067, 'Application Support Analyst', 'JM34223', 'permanent', 'Up to &pound;35k', '&lt;p&gt;They are looking for a talented French speaking Application Support Analyst, to join their team and be responsible for the support of their enterprise clients in France.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they have grown significantly globally, Derbyshire remains their head office which means that all future growth, progression, and projects will be in this Derbyshire based tech hub.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;It is an interesting time to join as they are now going through a huge transformation incorporating Agile / DevOps principles and modern technologies e.g. SaaS, Cloud and Microservices.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they are a global business, they are not corporate, maintaining a family-friendly working environment where work-life balance and employee wellbeing are key.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As an Application Support Analyst, you&nbsp;will work as part of a larger Application Support team and be responsible for supporting complex applications for some of their key clients in France.&nbsp;As well as it being important to provide tactful, insightful feedback to maintain a good working relationship with end users and other global product teams.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;There is an excellent opportunity for progression, with you in-charge of your own career path, as the company goes from strength to strength.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key Experience/Skills Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Fluent in French - This is essential&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;SQL / T-SQL&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Experience with ticketing systems (Freshdesk, Zendesk etc)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;TCP/IP&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;IIS&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Any experience of C# or ASP.Net would be highly advantageous&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary on offer is up to &pound;35,000 and comes with a comprehensive benefits package. Offices are commutable from Derby, Mansfield, Nottingham and they offer remote and flexible working.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;If this sounds like it would be perfect for YOU, then please apply!&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are currently working with a Derbyshire based Global SaaS&nbsp;Organisation who operate across North America, Europe, Middle East, Africa, and Australia.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|26||24|', 'application-support-analyst', 'yes', 'yes', 326, '', 1631567895, 1595289600),
(3068, 'Application Support Analyst', 'JM34223', 'permanent', 'Up to &pound;35k', '&lt;p&gt;They have an office based in Derbyshire but they are flexible with working and are happy to consider suitable candidates based within the UK that don&rsquo;t mind travelling to the Head Office infrequently whilst working remotely the majority of the time.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;It is an interesting time to join as they are now going through a huge transformation incorporating Agile / DevOps principles and modern technologies e.g. SaaS, Cloud and Microservices.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they are a global business, they are not corporate, maintaining a family-friendly working environment where work-life balance and employee wellbeing are key.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As an Application Support Analyst, you&nbsp;will work as part of a larger Application Support team and be responsible for supporting complex applications for some of their key clients in France.&nbsp;As well as it being important to provide tactful, insightful feedback to maintain a good working relationship with end users and other global product teams.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;There is an excellent opportunity for progression, with you in-charge of your own career path, as the company goes from strength to strength.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key Experience/Skills Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Fluent in French&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;SQL / T-SQL&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Experience with ticketing systems (Freshdesk, Zendesk etc)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;TCP/IP&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;IIS&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Any experience of C# or ASP.Net would be highly advantageous&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary on offer is up to &pound;35,000 and comes with a comprehensive benefits package.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;If this sounds like it would be perfect for YOU, then please apply below!&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a talented French speaking Application Support Analyst to join a global SaaS Organisation operating across North America, Europe, Middle East, Africa and Australia.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|24||26|', 'application-support-analyst', 'yes', 'yes', 0, '', 1631567895, 1595289600),
(3069, 'JavaScript Developer', 'SL34631', 'permanent', 'Up to &euro;100k', '&lt;p&gt;There is currently 4tb of storage and 1 minute time to confirm transaction finality, they want you to help get this to as close as zero!&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will work as part of a 2-person team supporting a larger 10 person agile squad to help work towards decentralized network neutrality. The Ethereum network is set to revolutionise how code and business logic is stored and smart contracts are authenticated across the Blockchain. The JavaScript team are responsible for taking what the larger team build and making it more accessible to the wider technical community, as Ethereum continues to adopt more users.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The organisation currently stands at 30 people, working in a modern, extremely agile way with a flat hierarchy. You will contribute to the open source community and ensure that as Ethereum continues to scale, latency does not stand in its way.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They are a team of world class engineers, who work extremely closely. Every day presents new challenges, where as a team new way of engineering are found to get closer to the organisations goals. You do not need prior experience of Blockchain but must have a passion for learning new technology and see the benefits it can bring to the world.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You will be an expert JavaScript engineer. Working with ES6 or Typescript and modern frameworks such at Vue, React, Angular and Node.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;An advocate of TDD.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;You are a big fan of github! Everything is checked in and tracked here.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A contributor to the open source community.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A real team player. Challenges of this magnitude are not solved alone!&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The organisation will have full support and training on anything you do not already know. Regularly support the team by attending conferences around the world and company treats which to date have been held in Japan, Mexico and the Philippines. They also have a company apartment in central Berlin readily available for anyone not local to Berlin but want to join the team in solving these exciting challenges.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I am recruiting for a Senior JavaScript Engineer to join a world class engineering team helping the Ethereum Blockchain network solve a critical challenge of reducing latency as it continues to scale and increase user adoption.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 20, '|7||8|', 'javascript-developer-sl34631', 'yes', 'no', 329, '', 1631567895, 1595980800),
(3070, 'Salesforce Developer', 'JM34817', 'permanent', '&pound;45k - &pound;65k', '&lt;p&gt;They are looking for a talented Salesforce Developer to join their team and be responsible for all of their clients Salesforce integrations.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Leeds is the companies services hub which covers the EMEA region and as such, has a healthy pipeline of new clients and projects. What this means for you is lots of exciting new work, opportunity to develop and progress within the company.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Due to increased client demand to integrate into the Salesforce ecosystem, the company are looking to hire their first Salesforce developer. You&nbsp;will work alongside a broad range including clients, the product development teams, but also with executives and board members.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for building the unique product templates into modern Salesforce environments to implemented across a range of enterprise clients. You will have the opportunity to shape all Salesforce integrations for the company and there are longer term opportunities to build a team around you.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they are a global business, they are not corporate, maintaining a family-friendly working environment where work-life balance and employee wellbeing are key.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key Experience/Skills Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; Salesforce Integration (2+ Years)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; APEX (e.g. utilising invokable apex, triggers, batchable and scheduled apex)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; SQQL&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; JavaScript&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; Visualforce&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Lightening (SLDS including JavaScript)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary on offer is between &pound;45,000 to &pound;65,000 (depending on experience) and comes with a comprehensive benefits package. They are hiring remotely and will offer flexible working.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I am recruiting for a Leeds based Fintech&nbsp;organisation who operate across North America, Europe, Middle East, and Africa.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|1||24|', 'salesforce-developer-', 'yes', 'no', 214, '', 1631567895, 1597017600),
(3071, 'Java Developer', 'JM34925', 'permanent', '&pound;35k - &pound;47,500k', '&lt;p&gt;They will be building a brand new, greenfield application which is fundamental to how the company runs and will be used by millions of people across the globe.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will get to work with the latest serverless technologies including Java, microservices, Node.js, Javascript, Typescript and AWS. As the Software Engineer you will significantly contribute to back-end, CI / CD, DevOps etc. They aren&rsquo;t looking for experience with all these skills, just solid experience with Java and modern processes such as TDD.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They have a great environment and a flexible and adaptable approach to technology, choosing the best tools for the job. They listen to the development team and their current technology stack includes numerous suggestions from within the dev team.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This is a rare opportunity as you will be working with zero technical debt, you will be building a best in class system from scratch which is scalable and highly available.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key experience required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Java&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Spring Boot&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Node.js&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;TDD&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;CI / CD&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;AWS&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Agile&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary for this role ranges from &pound;35,000 - &pound;47,500 and comes with a benefits package unrivalled in Leeds. It includes a 15% bonus and 10% pension contribution.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Please apply for a confidential discussion&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are currently working with a world leading Fintech organisation. They are looking to hire add a java developer to the highly agile squad.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 25, '|1|', 'java-developer-jm34925', 'yes', 'no', 199, '', 1631567895, 1597276800),
(3072, 'Test Practice Lead (Automation)', 'PC34953', 'permanent', '&pound;55k - &pound;65k', '&lt;p&gt;I am working in partnership with this brilliant business to recruit this role, which will take their team to the next level.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;After consistent year on year growth, my client is in an incredibly strong position and the Test Practice Lead role is a strategic hire to continue embedding quality in all that they do, and testament to the high standard of service that they are committed to delivering to their customers.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will lead and manage a team of 10 Testers across a range of enterprise products, focusing on their learning and development. You will be a Test Automation and Agile expert, passionate about using your experience to improve the skills of others.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As the Test Practice Lead, you will have the opportunity to make the role your own but be expected to champion best practice, lead by example, and shape / hone the future of testing within the business. This includes setting the standard and strategy for Test Automation, API Testing and Performance Testing, and bringing in new tools / technologies.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Skills and Experience Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Expert in Test Automation and industry standard tools such as Selenium Webdriver&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Proven recent hands-on experience with Automation Testing&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Strong knowledge of C# or Java&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Experience leading / managing teams of 8-10, OR currently managing a small team but keen to step up&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Agile&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Expert in QA best practice&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- First-class communication skills&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary on this position is &pound;55,000 - &pound;65,000, with a bonus and an excellent benefits package attached.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This is a unique opportunity that&#039;s not to be missed. You will inherit a team that are proactive, smart, and hungry to learn, and work alongside a team of Engineers that have brilliant minds as solve some really complex business challenges, delivering solutions that are used by MILLIONS of people all over the world.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Test Practice Lead required for a software house client in Leeds. Offices are easily commutable from Leeds, Wakefield, Doncaster, Castleford, Harrogate, and York.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 16, '|1||6|', 'test-practice-lead-automation--pc34953', 'yes', 'no', 202, '', 1631567895, 1597363200),
(3073, 'iOS Developer', 'PC34987', 'permanent', '&pound;40k - &pound;70k', '&lt;p&gt;My client is building a new mobile development team from the ground up and is looking for iOS Developers at all levels. As one of the first on the ground, you will play a key part in shaping and honing the culture of the business and what that looks like.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As an iOS Developer, you will enjoy solving complex problems such as stability, security and performance problems. You will have the opportunity to work with some truly brilliant Engineers, to build enterprise software applications that will be used by millions of people worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Skills and Experience required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- 3+ years&#039; experience in iOS Development&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Proficient in Swift or Objective C&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Agile delivery, CI/CD&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Development of large scale, enterprise applications&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary on these positions are dependent on experience but the right candidates can expect to earn around &pound;40,000 - &pound;70,000, with the top end of the salary range expected for candidates with architecture / leadership experience.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This is an excellent opportunity to join a hugely successful and profitable business with offices based globally. You will be challenged daily and given unrivalled opportunity to develop your skills and experience as an Engineer.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;iOS Developers&nbsp;required for a software house client in Sheffield.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 16, '|27|', 'ios-developer-', 'yes', 'no', 166, '', 1631567895, 1597708800),
(3074, 'Application Support Analyst', 'JM35004', 'permanent', 'Up to &pound;28k', '&lt;p&gt;They are looking for a talented Application Support Analyst, to join their team and be responsible for the support of their enterprise clients.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they have grown significantly globally, Derbyshire remains their head office which means that all future growth, progression, and projects will be in this Derbyshire based tech hub.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;It is an interesting time to join as they are now going through a huge transformation incorporating Agile / DevOps principles and modern technologies e.g. SaaS, Cloud and Microservices.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they are a global business, they are not corporate, maintaining a family-friendly working environment where work-life balance and employee wellbeing are key.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As an Application Support Analyst, you&nbsp;will work as part of a larger Application Support team and be responsible for supporting complex applications for some of their key enterprise clients.&nbsp;As well as it being important to provide tactful, insightful feedback to maintain a good working relationship with end users and other global product teams.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;There is an excellent opportunity for progression, with you in-charge of your own career path, as the company goes from strength to strength.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key Experience/Skills Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;SQL / T-SQL&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Experience with ticketing systems (Freshdesk, Zendesk etc)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;TCP/IP&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;IIS&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Any experience of C# or ASP.Net would be highly advantageous&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary on offer is &pound;28,000 and comes with a comprehensive benefits package. Offices are commutable from Derby, Mansfield, Nottingham and they offer remote and flexible working.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are currently working with a Derbyshire based Global SaaS&nbsp;Organisation who operate across North America, Europe, Middle East, Africa, and Australia.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|26||24|', 'application-support-analyst-', 'yes', 'yes', 63, '', 1631567895, 1597881600);
