(3075, 'Application Support Analyst', 'JM35004', 'permanent', 'Up to &pound;28k', '&lt;p&gt;We are currently working with a Derbyshire based Global SaaS&nbsp;Organisation who operate across North America, Europe, Middle East, Africa, and Australia.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they have grown significantly globally, Derbyshire remains their head office which means that all future growth, progression, and projects will be in this Derbyshire based tech hub.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;It is an interesting time to join as they are now going through a huge transformation incorporating Agile / DevOps principles and modern technologies e.g. SaaS, Cloud and Microservices.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Although they are a global business, they are not corporate, maintaining a family-friendly working environment where work-life balance and employee wellbeing are key.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As an Application Support Analyst, you&nbsp;will work as part of a larger Application Support team and be responsible for supporting complex applications for some of their key enterprise clients.&nbsp;As well as it being important to provide tactful, insightful feedback to maintain a good working relationship with end users and other global product teams.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;There is an excellent opportunity for progression, with you in-charge of your own career path, as the company goes from strength to strength.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key Experience/Skills Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;SQL / T-SQL&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Experience with ticketing systems (Freshdesk, Zendesk etc)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;TCP/IP&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;IIS&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Any experience of C# or ASP.Net would be highly advantageous&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary on offer is &pound;28,000 and comes with a comprehensive benefits package. Offices are commutable from Derby, Mansfield, Nottingham and they offer remote and flexible working.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;My client is&nbsp;looking for a talented Application Support Analyst, to join their team and be responsible for the support of their enterprise clients. This role is REMOTE!&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|24||26|', 'application-support-analyst-', 'yes', 'yes', 0, '', 1631567895, 1597881600),
(3076, 'Developer (C#.Net)', 'JM35048', 'permanent', '&pound;40k - &pound;50k', '&lt;p&gt;We are working in close partnership with a vibrant Leeds based company who are looking for several talented Developers to join their ever growing team.&nbsp;They have an immediate requirement to work on approved regulatory projects over the next 18 months.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The company have a flexible approach to the way they work and offer remote working for 2/3 days a week, giving you the perfect mix of interacting with team mates and having the flexibility to WFH.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The best thing about this organisation is that their Leeds based office is the software engineering centre of excellence for the northern hemisphere and their most exciting tech hub. And they have recently&nbsp;re-designed their systems and are moved them to a modern Azure Cloud and microservices architecture. This means that all growth, progression and future projects, using the latest technologies is based here in Leeds.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;What i love about this role is that you get the chance to join a well established team that are well versed in agile, DevOps and modern coding practices. Meaning you won&#039;t be only working with other developers, but alongside systems analysts, testers, architects and delivery managers to deliver high quality innovative software.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Technical knowledge and experience:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;SQL Server &ndash; writing stored procedures / views&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Knowledge of data warehousing concepts, data marts, dimensional data modelling and ETL processes.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Oracle&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;.NET / C#&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;SOLID principles&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Microsoft Azure (service fabric / storage)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Source control - GIT&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Unit Test Framework&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Mocking&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Restful API&rsquo;s&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot;Entity Framework / LINQ&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;***TO NOTE NOT ALL IS ESSENTIAL***&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The Salary for this role is between &pound;40,000 - &pound;50,000 dependent on experience and seniority, with flexible/remote working and a competitive package.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are working in close partnership with a vibrant Leeds based company who are looking for several talented Developers to join their ever growing team.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|24||13||6||14|', 'developer-c-net--jm35048', 'yes', 'no', 133, '', 1631567895, 1598313600),
(3077, 'Cloud DBA', 'jm35129', 'permanent', 'Up to &pound;70k', '&lt;p&gt;They have a flexible approach to the way they work and offer a flexible model with 2/3 days a week in office and the rest WFH, giving you the perfect mix of interacting with teammates and having the flexibility to WFH.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They are looking for an experienced Cloud DBA to work closely with the DevOps and Data Science teams to explore how data can be used across the business. This is more than a DBA role; you will be fundamental in moving the business from traditional on premise databases towards a cloud first database approach, utilising the full extent of AWS&rsquo;s capabilities. They will pay for your AWS certification&nbsp;exams and will also give you time off work to study / sit them.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;What I love about this role is that it is one of a kind where you will get the chance work closely with the CTO and have huge influence on all things data related, within a team of GO GETTING Tech professionals. Quoted from the CTO &quot;I want this person to not only be a knowledgeable professional but a real technology&nbsp;evangelist,&nbsp;who see&#039;s how using Tech and Data is the future&quot;.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The tech stack is below but as long as you have experience with AWS and a database background, they can teach you the rest;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; PostgreSQL/SQL Server/MySQL&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; AWS (Redshift, RDS, DMS)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; T-SQL&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; Performance Testing&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; Data Security&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&middot; Python (Not essential)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The Salary for this role is up to &pound;70,000 (dependent on experience), with a competitive package and flexible/remote working.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are currently working in close partnership with an organisation based in Leeds, who are looking for a passionate Cloud DBA to join their growing team.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|15||16||13||14|', 'cloud-dba-jm35129', 'yes', 'no', 52, '', 1631567895, 1599091200),
(3078, 'UX Designer', 'CP34531', 'permanent', '&pound;45k', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;!-- x-tinymce/html-mce_13568153911599212814209 --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The organisation already operate a flexible and modern approach to working with 2 &ndash; 3 days remote pre-covid.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Utilising cutting edge technology such as AI and Machine Learning the company are pushing the boundaries of entire industry, that effects millions of people daily.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be working on real time mission critical systems, challenging the status quo, and making a real difference to the industry by creating new ways to solve real problems&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The company has won a host of awards including the prestigious Queens award for enterprise. Due to this they are growing year on year and are now looking to add a UX designer to join the team.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As a UX Designer you will get the opportunity to make the role your own, they are looking for someone to take their award-winning product and make it something that is a joy to use.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Skills and Experience&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;3+ years plus &#039;UX&#039; Design experience as minimum.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Expereince conducting user research, competitor analysis and analysis data&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Good knowledge of user stories, personas, and storyboards.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Journey mapping. Information architecture. &ndash;&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;To conduct usability testing.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Have worked on Desktop, App and Dynamic Web sites.&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Created Wireframes&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Created Prototypes&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Excellent stakeholder management.&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This is a great opportunity to challenge yourself, make your mark in a growing company and on the world, and be rewarded for it&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Please apply for a confidential discussion&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;!-- x-tinymce/html-mce_13568153911599212814209 --&gt;We are currently working exclusively with an award-winning software house based in York, who are looking for a UX Designer.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', '', 0, 2, '|25|', 'ux-designer-2', 'yes', 'no', 37, '', 1631491200, 1599177600),
(3079, 'Data Engineer', 'JM35130', 'permanent', '&pound;35k - &pound;45k', '&lt;p&gt;The company have an excellent reputation for building and delivering complex data-driven software solutions for organisations looking to solve complex challenges with data.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They are looking to double in size in the next 2 years and you will be a key component of driving this growth.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;As a business they are true technologists; they choose the best tools for the job not just what&#039;s cool now. They are looking for someone who&#039;s passion aligns with this, you will ideally be an advocate of open source and an active contributor to the tech community.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;They currently have a need for people who are experienced with Python.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The key thing for them is that you&#039;re open to learning new technologies. As a business they use a variety of languages and technologies including Golang, Scala, Docker, Kubernetes, Hadoop, Kafka, Azure and AWS to name a few.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;If you want to work for a business where you progress quickly, work with a variety of the latest tech on enterprise projects then this is the role for you.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Key Skills Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Python&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;SQL&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;AWS&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Any experience with AI / Machine Learning would be a big advantage.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary for this position is up to &pound;35,000 - &pound;45,000.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;We are currently working with an award-winning software house based in Leeds that are looking to hire a Data Engineer.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 21, '|1||16||13||14|', 'data-engineer-', 'yes', 'no', 16, '', 1631567895, 1599436800),
(3080, 'Agile Business Analyst', 'DR35139', 'permanent', '&pound;40k - &pound;45k', '&lt;p&gt;This role is multi-faceted, engaging clients to spec out solutions whilst driving the product backlog internally with a team of talented software engineers.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;This organisation are multi award winners, known for their outstanding company culture that drives employee happiness and subsequently pushes their growth, supported by an outstanding leadership team.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Suitable candidates for this role must demonstrate the following experience:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;ul&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Business Analysis experience in an Agile environment&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Experience or product owner activities&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Experience working as part of a software engineering team&lt;/li&gt;\n	&lt;li&gt;Experience working with external customers&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The role is currently home based, with a blended home/office working practice in future.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary is flexible &pound;40-45k + benefits.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;As this organisation continue to thrive, there is an exciting opening for a talented Agile Business Analyst to join their product team.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 13, '|17|', 'agile-business-analyst-', 'yes', 'no', 40, '', 1631567895, 1599523200),
