(3084, 'Automation Tester', 'PC35056', 'permanent', '&pound;50k - &pound;55k', '&lt;p&gt;You will join a newly formed team in a start-up environment based in Leeds city centre.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;You will be joining a mobile native app team, but mobile automation experience is not essential providing you have experience building automation frameworks and are willing to learn.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Joining this business at the beginning of a journey, you will play a massive part in driving quality and technical excellence across mobile solutions that will be used by millions of people worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The progression opportunities in this role will be huge as you will join the team as their first Mobile Automation Tester. Because of this, you also will play a key part in shaping and moulding quality within mobile testing.&nbsp;Working alongside 1 other Tester, you will also have the opportunity to mentor and train them up on Test Automation, taking on more responsibility and growing the team.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;Skills and Experience Required:&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Experience developing robust and scalable automation frameworks in an Enterprise environment&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Strong knowledge of 1 or more programming languages (Java, C#, JavaScript, Python, etc.)&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Experience with industry standard automation test tools&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;- Agile, CI/CD&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;The salary on this position is &pound;50,000 - &pound;55,000 + 15% bonus and an excellent benefits package attached.&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;Automation Tester required for a global and highly reputable company.&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 16, '|1||6||8|', 'automation-tester-', 'yes', 'no', 0, '', 1631567895, 1599609600),
